enable_network_egress_export.description: Whether to enable network egress metering for this cluster. If enabled, a daemonset will be created in the cluster to meter network egress traffic.

enable_pod_security_policy.description: enabled - Enable the PodSecurityPolicy controller for this cluster. If enabled, pods must be valid under a PodSecurityPolicy to be created.

enable_private_endpoint.description: (Beta) Whether the master's internal IP address is used as the cluster endpoint

enable_private_nodes.description: (Beta) Whether nodes have internal IP addresses only

When enabled, a table will be created in the resource export BigQuery dataset to store resource consumption data. The resulting table can be joined with the resource usage table or with BigQuery billing export.

enable_vertical_pod_autoscaling.description: Vertical Pod Autoscaling automatically adjusts the resources of pods controlled by it
